A '''formal garden''' is a room in [[Player-owned house]], that can be built at level 55 [[Construction]] for {{Coins|75000}}, and has different decorations to the lower level [[garden]]. In addition, it does not have the tall grass that the lower level garden does.

For planting, the player needs to be holding a watering can (with water) in the player's inventory.

There are 8 [[hotspot]]s available:
*[[Big plant]]
*[[Big plant 2]]
*[[Centrepiece space]]
*[[Fencing]]
*[[Hedging]]
*[[Small plant]]
*[[Small plant 2]]
*[[Tip jar space]]

